Interface IBehaviorGuardEvaluatorReceiver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Agent, Behavior, Behavior, Behavior, BehaviorsSkill, DefaultContextInteractionsSkill, ExternalContextAccessSkill, FXBehavior, FXKillSupportBehavior, FXKillSupportBehavior, InnerContextAccessSkill, InternalEventBusSkill, LifecycleSkill, LoggingSkill, SchedulesSkill, Skill, Skill, Skill, Skill, Skill, Skill, Skill, Skill, Skill, Skill, TimeSkill

    public interface IBehaviorGuardEvaluatorReceiver
    Describes an object that has the ability to receive SARL events, and consequently to evaluate the guard associated to a given event and returns the list of behaviors' runnable that must be executed according to the result of the guard evaluation.
